ZH: 我们家的管家是个很有经验的人。
EN: Our family's butler is a very experienced person.

ZH: 请告诉管家准备晚餐。
EN: Please inform the butler to prepare dinner.

ZH: 这个管家非常照顾主人的需要。
EN: This butler takes great care of the needs of the master.

ZH: 他是个很周到的管家，总是能够满足主人的各种要求。
EN: He is a very attentive butler, always able to meet the various demands of the master.

ZH: 管家非常擅长布置宴会。
EN: The butler is very good at arranging banquets.

ZH: 我会找管家解决这个问题。
EN: I will ask the butler to resolve this issue.

ZH: 我们家的管家照顾家里的一切事务。
EN: Our family's butler takes care of all the household affairs.

ZH: 管家非常细心地整理了客人的房间。
EN: The butler carefully tidied up the guest's room.

ZH: 管家会在早上给您送早餐。
EN: The butler will deliver breakfast to you in the morning.

ZH: 管家每天会打扫整个庄园。
EN: The butler cleans the entire estate every day.

ZH: 这个管家是我们家族几代人都信赖的人选。
EN: This butler is a trusted choice for several generations of our family.

ZH: 管家会帮您安排行程和预订各种服务。
EN: The butler will assist you in arranging itineraries and booking various services.

ZH: 请管家备好我的行李。
EN: Please have the butler prepare my luggage.

ZH: 管家是家庭中非常重要的一员。
EN: The butler is a very important member of the family.

ZH: 管家会在您不在家时照顾花园和宠物。
EN: The butler will take care of the garden and pets when you are not at home.

ZH: 这个管家会给客人提供优质的服务。
EN: This butler will provide guests with excellent service.

