EN: I want to hire a butler to manage this mansion.

ZH: 管家会为您准备一杯热茶。
EN: The butler will prepare a cup of hot tea for you.

ZH: 管家是我们家庭的门面担当。
EN: The butler is the face of our family.

ZH: 我的朋友家的管家非常精明。
